## Responsive Design

### Mobile-First

```tsx
<div className="
  flex flex-col         {/* Mobile: stack vertically */}
  md:flex-row           {/* Tablet+: horizontal */}
  gap-4
  p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8     {/* Responsive padding */}
">
  <div className="w-full md:w-1/3">Sidebar</div>
  <div className="w-full md:w-2/3">Content</div>
</div>
```

